file.title: AMM PART II-1285 - CHAPTER 12-13-05-03 - LANDING GEAR TIRES - SERVICING

page.data: AIRCRAFT MAINTENANCE MANUAL LANDING GEAR TIRES - SERVICING EFFECTIVITY: ALL 1. General A. The procedures for the servicing on the landing gear tires is given in AMM TASK 32-49-01-600-801-A/300 (for the main landing gear) and AMM TASK 32-49-04-600-801-A/300 (for the nose landing gear).
